<chapter id="integrationwithothersoftware-integration" xreflabel="Integration Overview">
	<title>Integration Overview</title>
	<section>
		<title>Introduction</title>
		<para>One of the reasons that Nagios is such a popular monitoring application is 
the fact that it can be easily integrated in your existing 
infrastructure. There are several methods of integrating Nagios with the 
management software you're already using and you can monitor almost any type 
of new or custom hardware, service, or application that you might have.</para>
	</section>
